Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 13:56:58 +1200
Subject: [PATCH] Ubus: Add blobmsg_get_hex_string for parsing hex values

This replaces blobmsg_get_string + Hex2Bin.

Also don't accept ExtendedPanID's < 16 hex characters in "mgmtset" and
"setextpanid"; previously missing bytes were left uninitialized.
